    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m absolutely thrilled to show you this absolute gem. Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape that you\u2019d swear it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away in a garage and pampered with love. Not a single scratch or smudge to be found\u2014it's basically flawless. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve gotta come see this beauty in person. Let's get you behind the wheel! \u2728",
