    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8. This high-revving powerplant features an 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies, delivering linear power through a precise 6-speed manual transmission. Critical preventative maintenance has been proactively completed, including rod bearing replacement with VAC treated bearings and upgraded throttle actuators. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity with no subframe fatigue or bushing degradation. The exterior retains its original depth and luster with zero evidence of orange peel or clear coat failure. Inside, the Novillo leather remains supple with no bolster wear. This is a mechanically synchronized, turn-key example for the purist who demands an uncompromised driving experience.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
