      "description": "This pristine example has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The factory paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a professional ceramic coating with absolutely no rock chips or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather still carries its original aroma, and there is zero wear on the bolsters or touchpoints. Mechanically, it is flawless, backed by a comprehensive binder of every service record performed exclusively at the dealership. It drives exactly as it did the day it left the lot\u2014tight, responsive, and powerful. For the discerning collector who demands perfection, this is the one.",
