      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new? This car is an absolute dream! It\u2019s in flawless condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one, and it\u2019s been kept spotless inside and out. It drives like a charm and looks even better in person. I\u2019m really looking for someone who will appreciate such a well-kept beauty. Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come see it for yourself!",
