      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E46 M3 in collector-grade condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach: the rod bearings and VANOS system have been proactively addressed with documented service history, and the rear subframe has been fully reinforced to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The chassis remains taut, riding on a factory-spec suspension with zero bushing play or compliance issues. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via the Variable M Differential Lock, providing peerless corner-exit traction. The paint meter readings are consistent across all metal panels, and the interior retains its original factory matte finish with no bolster wear or upholstery fatigue. This is a turnkey, high-performance machine for the discerning enthusiast who demands mechanical perfection.",
